<title>
Sastavljanje i rastavljanje stražnjeg diferencijala
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A3206003">Uklanjanje i ugradnja sklopa stražnjeg diferencijala</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A3206004">Komponente stražnjeg diferencijala</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A3206005001">
<title>
Rastavljanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite prirubnice pogonskog vratila (1) sa stražnjeg diferencijala.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite poklopac diferencijala (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A320010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.252mm" ver = "01" gw = "109" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite uskočnike prirubnice pogonskog vratila.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite pogonski tanjurasti zupčanik s kućištem diferencijala.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite vijke pogonskog tanjurastog zupčanika (1), a zatim i pogonski tanjurasti zupčanik (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RS0D320010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "38.778mm" ver = "02" gw = "123" gh = "93"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite vanjske prstenove ležaja na strani diferencijala i unutarnje prstenove ležaja na strani diferencijala (1) s kućišta diferencijala koristeći specijalne alate.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3B001">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-60910">
09913-60910
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3B002">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-88210">
09925-88210
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RS0D320011.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.622mm" ver = "03" gw = "75" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izvucite zatik osovinice satelita specijalnim alatom i čekićem.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3B003">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-85811">
09922-85811
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RS0D320012.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.454mm" ver = "02" gw = "84" gh = "107"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izvucite osovinicu satelita i zatim uklonite zupčanike poluosovine (1), satelite (2), podložne pločice (3) i podloške (4) iz kućišta diferencijala (5).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RS0D320013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.994mm" ver = "02" gw = "126" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite brtvu i maticu stožastog zupčanika pomoću specijalnog alata i ključa s napajanjem (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3B004">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09930-40113">
09930-40113
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A320011.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.457mm" ver = "01" gw = "124" gh = "135"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite prirubnicu (1) s pogonskog stožastog zupčanika, a zatim izvucite pogonski stožasti zupčanik.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3B005">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-65135">
09913-65135
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
